A musical '''clinic''' is an informal meeting with a guest [[musician]], where a small-to-medium-sized [[audience]] questions the musician's styles and techniques and also how to improve their own skill. The musician might perform an entire [[Musical piece|piece]], or demonstrate certain techniques for the audience to observe. 

The objective is for the audience to learn from the guest musician. A musical clinic can apply to any type of [[musical instrument]], music or player. The clinics are often held at a musical instrument stores.

